OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLikely dry,
OL,6,Fwith cloud building through the
OL,7,Fevening, just a small chance of
OL,8,Fisolated thunderstorms across the
OL,9,Fsouthern Pennines early evening. Low
OL,10,Fcloud likely spreading inland
OL,11,Fovernight and accompanied by a
OL,12,Fstrengthening easterly breeze.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAny low cloud soon clearing
OL,15,Fto leave another dry day with good
OL,16,Fspells of sunshine. Feeling noticeably
OL,17,Fcooler in the brisk easterly breeze,
OL,18,Fthough still rather warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
